descript.abstract: Male - Female Ratio (layer) is a symbolized display presentation of the World countries 2004 and World CountryWatch Demographics (table) data sets. The geographic and attribute data of World countries 2004 and the joined World CountryWatch Demographics (table) are symbolized to create the layer. All features are symbolized as graduated colors based on the SEXRATIO00 attribute in the World CountryWatch Demographics (table).
